Package src.Entity

Class Staff

java.lang.Object
src.Entity.User
src.Entity.Staff
Direct Known Subclasses:
Administrator, Doctor, Nurse, Pharmacist
public abstract class Staff extends User
The Staff class is an abstract class that represents a staff member in the hospital system. It extends the User class and includes additional properties specific to hospital staff members, such as their role and age.
